"```sql\nSELECT DISTINCT c.UserDisplayName\nFROM comments c\nJOIN users u ON c.UserId = u.Id\nWHERE c.Score BETWEEN 1 AND 5\nAND u.DownVotes = 0;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the distinct display names of users who have made comments with a score between 1 and 5 and have 0 down votes. It joins the `comments` table with the `users` table using the foreign key relationship between `comments.UserId` and `users.Id`."